		"description": "<p>While you are in this stance and you are also Bloodied, all of your piercing or slashing weapon attacks deal an additional 1d4 points of ongoing damage to the target. This damage lasts for 1 minute or until an action is spent to stanch the bleeding. A single target can suffer from a number of instances of this ongoing damage equal to your Proficiency bonus, and each instance requires its own action to stanch. Creatures without blood are immune to this damage.</p>",
